records.Name: Uninsured Motorist
records.ProductDescription__c: Helps pay your medical expenses, lost wages and related damages if you're in an accident caused by a driver who doesn't have liability insurance.

records.Name: Medical Payments
records.ProductDescription__c: Covers medical costs after you are hurt in a car accident, regardless of who is found at fault for the accident, including coverage for your passengers.

records.Name: Comprehensive
records.ProductDescription__c: Covers damage caused by an event other than a collision, such as fire, theft or vandalism. If you hit an animal, or if your auto is flooded or stolen, Comprehensive coverage will apply.

records.Name: Comprehensive
records.ProductDescription__c: Covers damage caused by an event other than a collision, such as fire, theft or vandalism. If you hit an animal, or if your auto is flooded or stolen, Comprehensive coverage will apply.

records.Name: Collision
records.ProductDescription__c: Collision insurance is a coverage that helps pay to repair or replace your car if it's damaged in an accident with another vehicle or object, such as a fence or a tree
